title: Fake: You Are Not Dead: A Guide to Modern Living.
description:
Fake: You Are Not Dead: A Guide to Modern Living.

Greetings from the Fakeproject Corporation of America.

Following in the footsteps of some other great artists and fucking the recording industry, Fake is releasing their debut album online, free. There is no multilevel merchandising plan or handcuffing DRM?only high-quality, haunting music.

While essentially electronic, this isn&#039;t glitch, house, dance, trance, industrial, or eighties.  This isn&#039;t experimental, it&#039;s empirical becoming fact.  Fake stands apart, with stylistic influences stretching far and wide without imitation or mindless repetition?not of its inspirations, and not of itself. 

This album comes with a heavily illustrated PDF book, written in the style and tone of 1960&#039;s era US Government pamphlets, with instructions on how to live your life.

The torrent contains high-quality mp3s.  There is a preview of the album here:
 <a href="
http://www.fakeproject.com/you_are_not_dead/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.fakeproject.com/you_are_not_dead/</a>

You&#039;re invited to check it out. We doubt disappointment.
Thanks for downloading. D. Reetz and M. Holle
